{"tid":466952,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"竹園海鮮酒家","createTime":"2017-11-13T05:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T15:54:08.000Z","uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3da0ee00d934385cadaad8e42645f2958e164ef9","tid":466952,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/125619_a55e46e6f19d64b0677ce2e8e292c0f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F125619_a55e46e6f19d64b0677ce2e8e292c0f4.jpg&h=788f9793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n味道中上 價錢合理（～570一個人）同埋好多野送 又送小食 又送野喝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我好心痛 好多好食嘅酒樓冇乜人食（琴晚去食間野得2/3滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）反而啲劣食就大排長龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a1d077911deec24130e4a50097c600841b16b3","tid":466952,"uid":120854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d038a908815247f51ba27b8921238354f321693c","tid":466952,"uid":133563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:01:37.000Z","msg":"打手味濃。<br />\n<br />\n不過竹園真係好耐歷史。直家得返九龍城果間。"},{"pid":"81157d5e261bd0aac9a2b528d2a50d037bd626f8","tid":466952,"uid":98653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"上環???"},{"pid":"c488bde4c0afc0976acf58460fbf5e95590f476a","tid":466952,"uid":2655,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:02:19.000Z","msg":"$570一個人都叫合理<br />\n<br />\n窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e30510c0b6e3f2e5364fb70f0748992218df22","tid":466952,"uid":609,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"樓豬係南亞狗"},{"pid":"87a8daf5a09875e6b