","tid":466952,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上環???</blockquote><br />\n尖沙咀 個間 重慶大廈隔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n漢口道，<br />\n成日去飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲茶質素如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔錯，<br />\n每次飲茶一定會叫個例湯，<br />\n真心高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵日去試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b374fabd8ee4cec3886e6c16a5cb4f689a5273f","tid":466952,"uid":18948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:51:36.000Z","msg":"跑馬地果間係咪叫竹園？"},{"pid":"4667eb787b9a0859ffb329d5e3df4011b252e2c9","tid":466952,"uid":17404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:52:33.000Z","msg":"跑馬地電車總站有一間。<br />\n<br />\n以前造節有機會去。<br />\n<br />\n人多嗌到成張枱都係<br />\n<br />\n瀬尿蝦<br />\n<br />\n芝士龍蝦配蒜蓉包<br />\n<br />\n食水深係一jar jar嘅蔗汁橙汁<br />\n<br />\n好撚高質，建議嗌一碗潮州翅送黃芥辣(around hkd300)"},{"pid":"1543fa4c30d4f963f569fe57bfafb8c056c3275f","tid":466952,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:55:02.000Z","msg":"ALI點解你個po 有粒⭐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b2d30a865cda25978d1c578e01feb8166aa6e5","tid":466952,"uid":66099,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T07:04:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十仆南亞ching，狗也有分好壞</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face